{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"那就好。\n说实话，我一直担心让二年级学生担任学生会会长，是不是过早了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"…………","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event223-07-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"不过，看来是我杞人忧天了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"我记得……在你就任学生会会长的时候，\n校方就已经决定了要学生重新遵守之前形同虚设的校规了吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"嗯，是这样的","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event223-07-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"如果与自己生活密切相关的规则在没有事前通知的情况下\n突然发生了改变，一般人多少都会显露出反抗心","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"但是，你不一样。你没有一句怨言，就遵守了新的规定……\n这不是一件容易做到的事情","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":227,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":227,"voiceId":"event223-07-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"无论是否接受，我都会遵守规则。\n这就是我的原则","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event223-07-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":227}],"windowDisplayName":"理事长","body":"这样的信念很好。\n包括这次关于校外活动的讨论，你也做得很不错","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFac